---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="Lythaus privacy practices.">
  <section class="legal">
    <span class="pill">Legal</span>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="meta">Last Updated: February 2026 Â· Product: Lythaus</p>

    <h2>1. What we collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Account data</strong>: email address, authentication identifiers.</li>
      <li><strong>Profile data</strong>: username, bio, avatar URL.</li>
      <li><strong>Content data</strong>: posts, attached media URLs, moderation reports and appeals.</li>
      <li><strong>Technical data</strong>: push notification token, app/device metadata, security signals.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. Why we process data</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Provide core product features (feeds, posting, moderation, notifications).</li>
      <li>Enforce platform integrity and safety policy.</li>
      <li>Respond to legal obligations and abuse investigations.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Legal bases</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Contract performance for account and feature delivery.</li>
      <li>Legitimate interests for safety, abuse prevention, and reliability.</li>
      <li>Consent where required for optional analytics and marketing notifications.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>4. Data retention</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Inactive accounts: target deletion after 24 months.</li>
      <li>User-deleted content: target purge within 30 days.</li>
      <li>Moderation cases: retained through closure plus 90 days.</li>
      <li>Operational logs: short retention with minimization controls.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>5. Data subject rights</h2>
    <p>You can export or delete your data at any time from the Privacy Settings screen in the app, or by contacting us directly.</p>

    <h2>6. We don't sell your data</h2>
    <p>We do not sell personal information. We limit collection to what is needed to operate the service and comply with legal obligations.</p>

    <h2>7. Contact</h2>
    <p>Privacy inquiries: <a href="mailto:privacy@lythaus.app">privacy@lythaus.app</a></p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
